    "A total of 22 articles organized in 8 different clusters are linked among each other with 28 links (Figure 4B).",
    "The largest citation network is associated with Sallam (2023) with 13 links, followed by Biswas (2023) and Dwivedi et al. (2023a) with five links independently.",
